headline: Apartments.com Releases Multifamily Rent Report for the Fourth Quarter of 2024
summary: WASHINGTON, January 06, 2025--Today, Apartments.com – an online marketplace of CoStar Group, Inc. – published an in-depth report on multifamily rent trends for the fourth quarter of 2024.
